    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the absolute joy of driving it. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed, and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly stunning condition, inside and out, and drives like a dream. You won't find another one this well-loved in the neighborhood! Come by, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of it. It\u2019s ready for its next adventure!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
