    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a portal to a more elegant era. Cloaked in a deep, midnight sapphire that seems to drink the light, this masterpiece stands as a testament to timeless design. Slip into the cabin and you\u2019re greeted by the intoxicating aroma of hand-stitched, butter-soft cream leather that remains as supple as the day it left the workshop. Every curve of its pristine silhouette tells a story of weekend escapes to the coast and moonlit drives through rolling hills. When the engine awakens, it doesn't just start\u2014it breathes a low, melodic purr that promises effortless power and a soul-stirring connection to the road. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved legacy, a machine that captures the very essence of automotive perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
